{"tid":2219770,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"文匯報：Emilia「唔著」整月餅，再運到搣時潘的【情趣用品店】分銷","createTime":"2020-09-27T06:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T16:22:04.000Z","uid":79563,"like":26,"dislike":137,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"0caf81418abaae4bc853ba45687930c8bc366ac3","tid":2219770,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/12/173753/pic-70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F173753%2Fpic-70.png&h=0b988499&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n劉頴匡前女友、中文大學學生會前常務幹事黃于喬（Emilia Wong）亦在網上推銷其「自製」月餅，並在其社交媒體上載月餅的製作過程。雖然現時疫情尚未完全平息，惟從影片可見，黃在製作月餅時並無穿戴手套、口罩、髮網及圍裙等裝備。<br />\n<br />\n記者在購買有關月餅時發現，有關月餅的包裝並無標明食用日期及成分，職員在被追問時僅稱「自家買料自己整」，衞生安全成疑。記者付款後，被安排到攬炒派區議員劉家衡的「網紅」女友潘書韻（「搣時潘」）經營的情趣用品店取貨，並稱任何購買月餅的客人，購買情趣用品時可獲九折優惠。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wenweipo.com/a/202009/27/AP5f6fc676e4b0ac3aac4e7bd1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wenweipo.com%2Fa%2F202009%2F27%2FAP5f6fc676e4b0ac3aac4e7bd1.html&d=31jm0GaxjznMjcF0xOQh0pB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=0c458018\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wenweipo.com/a/202009/27/AP5f6fc676e4b0ac3aac4e7bd1.html</a>"},{"pid":"bb4986ad034013f33a8af352a2b4c145a2c3db73","tid":2219770,"uid":79563,"like":173,"dislike":3,"score":170,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:22:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黃在製作月餅時並無穿戴手套、口罩、髮網及圍裙等裝備。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nEmilia唔著, 係正常的"},{"pid":"d65ddf99ce378b2615facf662634d2762419fa91","tid":2219770,"uid":52194,"like":22,"dislike":3,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:22:45.000Z","msg":"夾奶賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a57d1c182d17c8d50c15b16878d5d263630e0f3","tid":2219770,"uid":53122,"like":40,"dislike":4,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:23:22.000Z","msg":"多謝賣廣告<br />\n<br />\n即刻想食<img src=\"/assets/fac